sec.p:
The primary outcomes for this study were mean Relative Dietary Energy Adequacy Ratio (RDEAR) between pregnant women and the male household heads and mean RDEARs between pregnant women and their mothers-in-law, as defined in the following equation:
(1)\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
